The paper proposes a new active learning scheme for hypergraphs, which is a topic related to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses theoretical results on the query complexity, which is related to data structures (cs.DS) and computational complexity (cs.CC). Additionally, the paper introduces a novel parametric system, which could be considered as a topic related to systems and control (cs.SI).
